{"tid":1694421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"6/11 Sogo感謝節齊齊和你shop","createTime":"2019-11-05T06:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T06:54:02.000Z","uid":77383,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"fd3b77a6369f282be1d7cf4952701532d7882e77","tid":1694421,"uid":77383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:59:59.000Z","msg":"Sogo作為購物聖地， 對零售業既經濟效益可謂有重大貢獻！<br />\n我地香港人決定係Sogo感謝節期間感謝返佢，大家食左tg又戴左咁耐口罩皮膚差左，一齊去買返啲護膚品都好正常啫。天氣轉涼，上多幾層就有新衫買。真係諗起都興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解要6/11去？星期六日唔係好啲咩？<br />\n當然唔係，入面做嘅同事話你知第一日既營業額係最高最多人排隊，香港人執輸行頭慘過敗家，點可以輸比班自遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去銅鑼灣定尖沙咀？<br />\n去完一間再去一間都得啫，有啲產品係銅鑼灣/尖沙咀限定。睇清楚自己想要啲咩咪得囉<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/duAdGSS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FduAdGSS.png&h=bd52f809&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8FhccZy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8FhccZy.png&h=241fbcdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我個人就私心想見到CWB個經理仆街<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ewXvJ6R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FewXvJ6R.png&h=088a4996&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/onyVVdx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FonyVVdx.png&h=e5a75177&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bCXGQMS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbCXGQMS.jpg&h=5fecdfa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要準備啲咩？<br />\n記得帶環保袋呀，最好啲品牌紙袋<br />\n我地好環保架嘛<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3F9FmTG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3F9FmTG.jpg&h=00e310b6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/74ERtyH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F74ERtyH.jpg&h=8dadf024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啲老闆好鍾意見到大家一袋二袋架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/44eerkz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F44eerkz.jpg&h=a06c1e28&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D3pxXsf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD3pxXsf.jpg&h=a2daef01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係門口排隊會唔會被人話非法集結架？<br />\n你咪試下囉，睇下班蝗以後嚟唔嚟購物，最好無差別扑鳩埋佢地。Sogo多得你唔小，仲可以比班蝗/水貨佬試下tg既滋味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ae8yGT6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fae8yGT6.png&h=ad1dc101&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好唔記得最底嗰層有citysuper <br />\n佢地啲試食產品又多又好食，買之前都要試下好唔好食架嘛係咪<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ORHAeo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ORHAeo.png&h=4f27f4da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n10:00朝早開門，同以往一樣應該朝早8點左右已經有人/蝗排隊架啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\ncap定啲圖比大家做個參考下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cCTnAff.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcCTnAff.png&h=ad820a90&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dKC0mVh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdKC0mVh.png&h=aedeb0d2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W7n7Mm5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW7n7Mm5.png&h=db98609f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後祝大家購物愉快</span></span>"},{"pid":"9427414d76a46c51de2eb5534e2c12a4ea4f82bd","tid":1694421,"uid":77383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:01:26.000Z","msg":"推推囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f29dfc66379f80cd11c2c2bfb42fe74a2fcbcb","tid":1694421,"uid":77383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2